divs: Sighting DetailsHere's a couple pics straight from the backyard at around 9pm. Object in question is just to the left of street lamp in photo's. Stationary for hours. Blinks red and white and or blue and white and level of intensity seems to really change. One minute it looks huge and very bright in the sky and the next appearing very small and dim and others completely out of sight for minutes at a time and then turning back on.
Summary: Fake Star, Planet , ufo or what
